query: SELECT m.name, m.category, m.totalCarbon, r.risScore, r.lisScore, (r.risScore - r.lisScore) as netImpact FROM materials m JOIN risScores r ON m.id = r.materialId ORDER BY (r.risScore - r.lisScore) DESC LIMIT 5;
